                            <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/1450">Shapor, bishop of Niqator</persName> is commemorated in <title ref="http://syriaca.org/work/261">Shapor, Isaac, Maʿna, Abraham and Simeon (text)</title>.</p>
                    </event>
